  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Synergy Private Equity Fund Limited</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Fund is expected to have significant development impact on its investees by - providing them with risk capital coupled with management advice in their expansion plans; - implementing best practice Environmental, Social and Governance at both the Fund and Investees; and - stimulating job creation by supporting fast growing companies.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project is an equity investment in Synergy Private Equity Fund (SPEF or the Fund), a 10 year closed-end generalist private equity fund targeting fast-growing small and medium sized enterprises in Nigeria and  Ghana The Fund is seeking to raise up to $75 million total committed capital.  The Fund will make equity and quasi-equity investments of up to $10 million each in fast-growing SMEs, primarily through acquisition of significant minority stake in the businesses.</narrative>
  </description>
